30 (a) The defendant is concurrently or consecutively sentenced to
31 imprisonment for any felony other than another Class IV felony;
-16-

LB1020 LB1020
2026 2026
1 (b) The defendant has been deemed a habitual criminal pursuant to
2 section 29-2221; or
